snippet.title: 6-Sided Stories | Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
A look at the gameplay from 6-Sided Stories, a cozy and relaxing puzzle game by DarZal Games.

Releasing on Steam November 20th, 2024.
FREE DEMO available now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2785330/6Sided_Stories


Music: Faithful Mission & A Wavy Night's Breath by Artificial.Music https://artificialaryll.bandcamp.com/music
